text: Food is definitely good. can customise for less salty/spicy. store operator is very friendly.

Hardworking family working from early lunch when most stores are closed, very admirable. Our family always gets the basile chicken/pork. Today we of course the basile chicken again and a sauteed kangkong, great portion and value. Thank you!!

The mom and dad have great service and food but omg.. i ordered fried rice with chicken, the son ordering from me served me prawn, its fine because i noticed it so i asked then to change

Then i went home and realized a white rice was missing from my order which i paid $1 for! This is so infuriating
Deep fried pork strips awesome. Tomyum soup and Sotong not bad. Lala sauce was too diluted for some reason, Omelette so not worth it and plain, can cook your own at home.

Pineapple rice was well fried, not too oily and topped with pineapples, raisins, cashew nuts and chicken floss. Tom yum soup tasted sour and it wasn't spicy at all.  It was awesome and price was reasonable too.
